.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, drama, action
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
5. the fan of blues is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts | action | drama | zombie |

