.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, camping, photography, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is camping##7
2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7
4. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | camping   | photography | rock-climbing | filmmaking    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

