2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person eating pumpkin##8
6. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Food   | pumpkin      | garlic | apricot | peach   |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing | volleyball  | cricket |

