4. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
6. the person watching family movies is not the person driving the taxi##6
7. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
8. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
