4. the person eating watermelon is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating raspberry is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating plum##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | raspberry | plum         | mango    | watermelon       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

