.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: french, colombian, japanese, malaysian
 1. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the japanese##1
 4. the japanese is not to the right of the colombian##8
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the japanese##8
 9. the colombian is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the french##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Nationality   | french | malaysian  | japanese     | colombian    |

