.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, trike
1. the person drinking coffee is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking coffee##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage         | fanta  | coffee | juice  | hot-chocolate  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

