.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, videographer, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not the freelancer##6
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the writer is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the videographer is the person driving the car##1
5. the writer is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the car##7
6. the writer is on the left of the freelancer##1
7. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the van and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur    | writer | freelancer | videographer |
| Transport   | jet-ski | van      | subway     | car     |

 